MODIFICATIONS FROM ORIGINAL:

This operator has been adapted from the CloudNativePG operator for use with
the Flagsmith feature flag platform. Major modifications include:

1. Replaced PostgreSQL cluster management with Flagsmith instance deployment
2. Added Flagsmith Management API client integration
3. Created new CRDs for Flagsmith resources:
   - FlagsmithProject
   - FlagsmithEnvironment
   - FlagsmithFeatureFlag
   - FlagsmithSegment
   - FlagsmithApproval
4. Integrated Helm for Flagsmith deployment
5. Added approval workflow and governance features
6. Integrated with Kyverno policy engine
7. Added Slack and Email notification support

The core reconciliation patterns, controller framework, and infrastructure
code are derived from CloudNativePG. All Flagsmith-specific business logic
is original work.

